{"tid":1591121,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"公義何在】上屆傘兵被抹黑成建制，有人可以幫手嗎？","createTime":"2019-09-24T04:34:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T14:33:45.000Z","uid":15428,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5ffa78ac822dd15e05f9cde47d358362d462c7f1","tid":1591121,"uid":15428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T04:34:51.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我都知呢個時候唔應該講選舉<br />\n而選舉制度都真係fail<br />\n但係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「自己地區自己救」</span></span></strong>我相信唔係淨係叫口號（同光復香港一樣！）<br />\n<br />\n入正題先！尋晚有街坊send畀我睇相信係有人整區選嘅database...但指上屆傘兵係建制獨立候選人，我知好多人都唔睇返過去發生咩事，但可唔可以唔好咁唔公平？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可唔可以幫手更正返呢啲database<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者幫我搵到源頭⋯⋯我自己搞<br />\n（因為我一個人已經做唔到太多嘢啦，咁多條戰線）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vd5bNjC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVd5bNjC.jpg&h=2e2313f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5YC19x7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5YC19x7.png&h=77c5c801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.<br />\n譚香文嗰個反自動當選fb page+excel長期唔update兼錯"},{"pid":"3120dc45237c9c7edab751005bd6fab722b003e1","tid":1591121,"uid":15428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:10:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2869d45c9dfb873e17274c88706b6880ca8f7cbd","tid":1591121,"uid":15428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:34:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545616/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545616/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有冇人搵到呢個post嘅樓主「自由奶閪」？</span></span>"},{"pid":"c9675a6b0bdfe1ed4ce6fa8105dc1b66b720b97e","tid":1591121,"uid":91397,"l