"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:41:43.000Z","msg":"呢壇野我記得, 上屆祥華果隻白鴿夾埋祥華法團同林卓庭一齊搶左個議席, 果隻白鴿陳旭明搶左個位黎做之前又應承幫手攪掂單水管事件, 點知而家單野用左條友講既不變應萬變拖左幾年之後而家俾人告到要賠成二千幾萬好似, 但最慘祥華班廢老仲係好支持佢<br />\n最撚惱係陳旭明最近成日想要抗爭者支持, 走埋去連儂牆果度鳩遊行就當做左野食人血饅頭, 呢條仆街勁可恥"},{"pid":"f9ee4f3f60ced6d1b5d2ddcbd584350f34d60451","tid":1591121,"uid":72602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:41:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U0bROga.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU0bROga.jpg&h=5e267a10&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa5c3657fd5dcd8c49fde8bb943531245503b7b2","tid":1591121,"uid":15428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:41:58.000Z","msg":"講就講<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">齊上齊落</span></span><br />\n到頭來都係散水，究竟有冇人諗過直接企埋同一陣線，而唔係捐錢捐飯劵就已經當為香港出咗力<br />\n慢慢開始會明白點解香港會令人絕望⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a864a027b51f878c236616d9190eacff75e7ecb","tid":1591121,"uid":42007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:42:41.000Z","msg":"咪又俾民主派收割"},{"pid":"e5509579b5f7fe60ebcf5cbe930c6c497698ffdf","tid":1591121,"uid":15428,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9ee4f3f60ced6d1b5d2ddcbd584350f34d60451","tid":1591121,"uid":72602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:41:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U0bROga.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU0bROga.jpg&h=5e267a10&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:42:59.000Z","msg":"左膠式嘅紀念日不了，係做嘢嘅就好好儲你嘅魔法值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d099c6a854b0c63163bd951f658ae8604c30555","tid":1591121,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:43:20.000Z","msg":"個PAGE好似係自由系搞，最少見到佢SHARE，大野君你不如聯絡下ADMIN"},{"pid":"4720b5c00c6d0ce2c2d7e4a778c5591c3f9da06a","tid":1591121,"uid":86314,"like